== Overview ==
The MegaCorp experimental XG56D series 45 beta prototype Rail-Gun has had some serious development problems over its 32 year design period. Now however it is considered the replacement technology for heavy caliber guns and cannons.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Rail-Gun can be bought in the workshop or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in Vulcore.
